schools out, i am no longer forced to socialize.

sweet.


i am sitting next to my boyfriend, but i dont think he knows that i am here... the pistons are on. they dont get respect.

neither do i.


but at least i have dr. pepper and hit the lights.

my light burned out today, and i sat there in the dark and cried about it, i dont understand these feelings, it is just so hard to be depressed all the time. 

i hate my parents, they bought me a stupid 2004 grand prix... i asked for a fkn 2005, i am moving out as soon as i can. they just dont understand me. no one does. 

i decided that i am no longer going to brush my hair, its so over-rated, i like it much better matted with knots, i'll just put what i can into pigtails, i <3 bleach. i <3 hairspray. i </3 hairbrushes. 

and i love taking pictures of myself as long as the camera is tilted 45 degrees and it shows my left eyeball, it's the better one, ya kno.
i hate baskin robins. it is the cause of all pain and misery.

you kno what i just realized? 



my only friends are the lj maintence guys.



i dont even like them anyways.



my life sucks.

i havnt updated in a while, but its not like anyone cares anyways



ive been really busy lately listening to brand new, and going to local concerts that i dont have time to write. 


i got my lip pierced today, it looks rad, its a little red and swollen, and seems to be oozing some green shit, but it ok, cuz it looks RAD. 
i think my boyfriend will want to kiss me more bcuz i have it, even tho he thought it was a piece of food the first couple times he kissed me. gross. 


i smoked my last cigarette today, i got really pissed. i was having the worst day ever, then i decided to get some tbell, so i threw my cigarette out the window and it came back in, and got stuck in the hood of my hoodie. it burnt a hole in my favorite hoody. it made me mad. i couldnt help but to cry. my dad always said i only get one tear, so i better make it good. well hes the cause of all my problems now. hes why i cry. 






thanks dad. 




but i think i'm gonna go drink some jones soda and sit in my darkened room.
